examples.en: Shrinkage is the retail trade's euphemism for shoplifting.
...if we catch you shoplifting again, we're going to run you in...
The teenager caught shoplifting seemed to evince no remorse.
Convictions for shoplifting have made it difficult for her to get a job.
Being contrite is not enough to spare you an arrest if you're caught shoplifting.
The judge refused to allow mention of the defendant's conviction for shoplifting, ruling that it was inapplicable to the case at hand.
an advanced case of avidity that led to shoplifting at the tender age of 13
